# xiaomi-gamepad: per-game gyro / tilt-aim.
#
# List the games that should get accelerometer tilt-aim -- ONE process-name substring per line.
# While a process whose command line contains one of these substrings is running, pad tilt drives
# the right stick. Games NOT listed here (e.g. GTA) never get gyro, and the pad is never written to
# on their behalf. Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored. The list is re-read live,
# so edits take effect within a couple of seconds -- no daemon restart needed.
#
# Find a running game's process name with, e.g.:   pgrep -fa <name>
# For Wine/Proton games it's usually the .exe name (e.g. "Game.exe").
#
# Examples -- DELETE these and add your own games:
# SuperTuxKart
# Game.exe
